    "last_edit_date" : 1543058605,
    "creation_date" : 1376670081,
    "answer_id" : 18277912,
    "question_id" : 18274031,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Almost everything in the smali language has a direct analogue in the dalvik bytecode or dex format.</p>\n\n<p>The .line directive in particular corresponds to the position entries emitted by the state machine that the debug_info_item defines, as specified at <a href=\"https://source.android.com/devices/tech/dalvik/dex-format\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://source.android.com/devices/tech/dalvik/dex-format</a>.</p>\n"
  } ],
